               <text xliff:rid="51675F5A-466E-4E1D-A458-9ED6DD40EB90">We thank you for the above purchase order and issue our acceptance of the same subject to the terms and conditions already given in our quotation and those given below and overleaf. This order is subject to force majure clause. </text>
