            <value>
               <exData contentType="text/html" xliff:rid="A7A9AB8A-66F7-4D5D-8FE1-79B16041AF24">
                  <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xfa="http://www.xfa.org/schema/xfa-data/1.0/"><p style="letter-spacing:0in">____________________________________________________________________________________________________</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Final Amount<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField021726" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">P &amp; F Charges<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField019912" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/> %</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">GST Applicable as per GST ACT 2017. (Only for deomestic customer)<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">   </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">____________________________________________________________________________________________________</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Amount in words<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField018716" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Terms Of Payment<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField025667" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Insurance<span style="xfa-tab-count:2">                  </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField023281" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Mode Of Despatch<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField002995" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Documents Through<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField017421" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Special Instructions<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField014771" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">ENDPROTECT</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">PROTECT</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">____________________________________________________________________________________________________</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Our Bank Details:</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">State Bank of India</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Commercial Branch, Office No: 101 &amp; 102, Next Gen Avenue, Bahiratwadi, Senapati Bapat Road, Pune-411 016<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Account No: 31115928484, Branch Code:04108 SWIFT Code : SBININB<br/>____________________________________________________________________________________________________</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">____________________________________________________________________________________________________</p><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">                                                                                                                           </span><span style="font-weight:bold">For Delval Flow Control Pvt. Ltd.<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">         </span></p><p style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">                                                                                                                     </span></p><p style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">                                                                                               </span>Authorised Signatory</p><p style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in">____________________________________________________________________________________________________</p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">C.S.T. Number/Date<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">L.S.T. Number/Date<span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="letter-spacing:0in">Excise Number<span style="xfa-tab-count:2">                  </span>:</p><p style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in">____________________________________________________________________________________________________</p><p style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span>In case of any descripancies please contact salesindia@delvalflow.com.<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">  </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in">F/CRM/02 REV.00<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">         </span>Phone: +91-9763720100/9763661000<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">   </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="margin-bottom:1.44pt;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">                                          </span></p><p style="margin-bottom:1.44pt;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="margin-bottom:1.44pt;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">                                          </span>(This is computerised statement and does not require a Signature)<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">   </span></p></body>
